Details:
Team size : 5
Counter Strike GO

 desc:Counter-Strike (officially abbreviated as CS) is a series of multiplayer first-person shooter video games, in which teams of terrorists and counter-terrorists battle to, respectively, perpetrate an act of terror (bombing, hostage-taking) and prevent it (bomb defusal, hostage rescue).
     
Rules:
1. Players can bring their own mouse pads, keyboard headphones and other peripherals to stimulate their own best playing environment.
2. Tournament format 5 v 5
3. Maps will be decided on spot
4. All matches will consist of 14 rounds, out of which each team will be CT and Terrorists for 7 rounds.
